--[[
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║         NO-BREAKJOINTS CBRING — VISUAL INDICATOR + LIVE CONFIG UI           ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

  Two additions over the base model:

  1. VISUAL INDICATOR
     A SelectionSphere anchored to the tool Handle showing the current
     reach radius.  Color shifts:
       Gray   → script disabled
       Green  → enabled, no targets in range
       Yellow → one or more targets within range (pre-drag)
       Red    → drag actively executing this frame

  2. LIVE CONFIG PANEL
     A draggable ScreenGui with real-time sliders and toggles for every
     CFG value.  Changes apply immediately — no reload required.
     Includes a live stats strip showing session kills, avg distance,
     and last victim.

  Architecture note:
     All UI and visualizer code is client-local.  Nothing here changes
     what the server sees.  The config panel modifies CFG values in
     getgenv() so they persist across coroutines and can be read by the
     heartbeat loop on the same frame.
--]]

